data.description: Newly listed in Brookhaven At Durham Lakes in Fairburn! Explore this stunning two-story home boasting 6 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, situated on a spacious corner lot. Enjoy a grand Formal Dining Room, Living Room/Opt. Study, and Very Large Kitchen with massive island overlooking the Breakfast Room and Family Room with Fireplace. The first floor also includes a Mud Room, Pantry, and a Downstairs Bedroom with a Private Full Bath. Upstairs, discover a Laundry Room, Four Secondary Bedrooms, Two Secondary Bathrooms, and a lavish Owner's Suite featuring a Sitting Room, Large Walk-In Closet, and Private Owners Bath. Large flat yard for all your entertaining needs! Don't miss this amazing home!!
